	&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size:13.5pt;font-family:inherit, serif;color:#0B2135;&quot;&gt;We will take reasonable measures to require that the party receiving any of your Personal Information undertakes to: (i) retain and use such information only for the purposes set out in this Privacy Policy; (ii) not disclose your Personal Information except with your consent, as permitted by law, or as permitted by this Privacy Policy; and (iii) generally protect the privacy of your Personal Information.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 
